{"tid":1808587,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"攝影師11 月拍攝反政府示威後，伏屍家中且相機失踪而至今無人被捕","createTime":"2020-01-02T12:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T13:20:20.000Z","uid":2748,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"211f12d7b51e67a281def4ee387f5292c22c058b","tid":1808587,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://photoblog.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/death01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fphotoblog.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2Fdeath01.jpg&h=8a471bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日香港元旦大遊行，仍有數以十萬甚至上百萬的示威者上街，持續著爭取五大訴求的運動；而遠在地球另一邊的智利，早前仍持續有激烈衝突甚至示威者死亡，更有發現當地一名攝影師 ，在拍攝一場示威活動後，倒斃家中，身體呈現被毆打痕跡，裝著其電腦、手機及相機的袋子亦失去踪影，估計正是與她拍攝的示威有關。<br />\n<br />\n據當地及多個媒體報導，在去年11月21日，一位居於智利首都聖地牙哥的攝影記者 Albertina Mart&iacute;nez (上圖)，於死前兩日拍攝了一場反政府示威，雖然事件被警方視為一般劫殺案，但由於拍攝的時機加上照片不見了，令人質疑她的死因與示威相關。當地攝影記者組織 Frente Fotografic&oacute; 則以上載死者的作品，並附以 #JUSTICIAPARAALBERTINA 來回應其死亡，並希望當局能徹查事件並還原失踪的資料，但直至今天仍未有人因此被捕，亦沒有檢控官與死者家人聯絡過。<br />\n<br />\n報導指攝影師從十年前開始，從智利南部移居聖地牙哥，並且於當地主要報章《El Mercurio》工作，然後再轉到電視台擔任燈光助理。而攝影師曾向朋友表示，雖然很害怕，不過仍然喜歡去拍攝示威現場。<br />\n<br />\n根據無國界記者的「新聞自由指數」，智利在 2019 年於 180 個國家中排名 46，算是比較上遊的位置 (香港則跌至 73 位，比非洲的塞內加爾和科特迪瓦更低)，不過近月來智利警察對記者越來越敵視，更會以警棍、子彈、催淚彈及水炮等攻擊攝影師，並且毀掉他們的攝影器材，對香港人來說這些事件恐怕都絕不陌生。"},{"pid":"3262173c80edf037b6a5e38eb35038f670768ee0","tid":1808587,"uid":2748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:51:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/dec/31/chile-photographer-albertina-martinez\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2F2019%2Fdec%2F31%2Fchile-photographer-albertina-martinez&d=lD%2FUaJpd7HswZ4lFnFCcPqwVmkNCIo3TbJkxuaymrXU%3D&h=edb5782e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/world/2019/dec/31/chile-photographer-albertina-martinez</a>"},{"pid":"29762a6953e29a6487764bba455eaa5d5c38d6bf","tid":1808587,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:52:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">含撚啦泛民打手！<br />\n［最後通牒］警告泛民重回正軌 否則勇武將會全面退場攬炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1808373\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1808373</a></span></strong>"},{"pid":"93a68c5a461c6fb617d10e1e95caa423f4af41ca","tid":1808587,"uid":291065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"講清楚啦屌"},{"pid":"6b60bb4ebedb0d978a683e5e77a9396df4c920ff","tid":1808587,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"嚇撚得我以為又有手足死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5838623fc532033db11115ee16560e35e55054d6","tid":1808587,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:53:39.000Z","msg":"好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4693c4fc4643aa57433b79c594f0c90589d98a3d","tid":1808587,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:54:33.000Z","msg":"RIP"},{"pid":"5d69dc5672a980c6b1d11b7f8196414f62092281","tid":1808587,"uid":255557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"我覺得香港記者要小心自己<br />\n唔好比狗毁屍滅跡...."},{"pid":"3ad56d4d331b389b7e7cacfe1fca75c904584fae","tid":1808587,"uid":290393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b60bb4ebedb0d978a683e5e77a9396df4c920ff","tid":1808587,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"嚇撚得我以為又有手足死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T13:20:20.000Z","msg":"唉 智利人死 都會唔開心<br />\n<br />\n雖然好彩